impactDescription: I strongly believe that with my various activities on op chain by trading, buying and selling of tokens,  minting of nfts under optimism chain,,,bored app etc, also I keep optimism chain active by making transactions under op chain u can track my wallet to confirm, I don't stay a week without transactions on op chain...I also use various contracts on op chain, stake op, I provide liquidity under op chain as well using stargate, op to me remains the best and cheaper chain to transact on, I strongly belive that my daily and weekly transactions under op chain adds to the contribution of optimism. contributionDescription: To be very sincere I needed this RetroPGF badly., I joined optimism few years back and I have been very active on the chain...you can track my activities through the address I already dropped under payout address., even since I joined optimism I have been using the bridge through different site, e.g stargate, woofi, uniswap, sushi and velodrome...I made varieties of trades under optimism because its network is very fast and cheap as well. I will describe my contribution to optimism below,,I staked my op, I trade op on exchanges, I did the op quest about 18 nfts and above all I give out op gas fees to anyone in need..by so doing I show my support to the great optimism chain. Thanks bosses 🙏🏻
